<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Our Book Community!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 8px; /* Added border radius to the logo */
    }

    .welcome-message {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0066cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .social-links a {
      margin: 0 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
  <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Book Community Logo" class="logo">
  <h1>Welcome to Our Book Community!</h1>
</div>

<div class="welcome-message">
  <h2>Hello {{userName}}!</h2>
  <p>Thank you for joining our book community. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
  <p>Your account has been successfully created with the email:
    <strong>{{userEmail}}</strong></p>
</div>

<h3>What you can do now:</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Browse our extensive collection of books</li>
  <li>Join discussions about your favorite titles</li>
  <li>Place bids on rare editions</li>
  <li>Share your reviews and ratings</li>
  <li>Connect with fellow book enthusiasts</li>
</ul>

<p>To get started with your book journey, click the button below:</p>
<center><a href="{{exploreUrl}}" class="button">Explore Now</a></center>

<p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team at
  <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>

<div class="personal-touch">
  <p>We've handpicked some recommendations based on your preferences:</p>
  <ul>
    {{#each bookRecommendations}}
      <li><strong>{{this.title}}</strong> by {{this.author}} - {{this.genre}}</li>
    {{/each}}
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="social-links">
  <p>Follow us to stay updated:</p>
  <a href="{{facebookUrl}}">Facebook</a>
  <a href="{{twitterUrl}}">Twitter</a>
  <a href="{{instagramUrl}}">Instagram</a>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Book Community. All rights reserved.</p>
  <p>
    <small>
      You received this email because you signed up for Book Community.
      <br>
      To unsubscribe, <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">click here</a>
    </small>
  </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>